Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Could you stop it for now?}{\i0}Cô dừng lại chút đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Um, I've got to go save her.}{\i0}Tôi sẽ đi cứu cô ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh?}{\i0}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I have to go rescue the owner of this voice.}{\i0}Tôi phải giải cứu chủ nhân của giọng nói này.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hold up.}{\i0}Khoan đã.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.59,0:00:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Don't be so hasty.}{\i0}Đừng có dễ tin vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{For one thing, there's no telling\Nwho might be seeking help, you know.}{\i0}Với cả chưa biết cô ấy\N có đang tìm kiếm sự giúp đỡ không?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.43,0:00:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's too risky!}{\i0}Nó quá mạo hiểm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But—}{\i0}Nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hai người...{Hey, you two...}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What's going on?}Gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess...}{\i0}Jess...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Please save me. I'm begging you.}{\i0}Xin hãy cứu tôi, làm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Please save me from this terrifying darkness.}{\i0}Xin hãy cứu tôi khỏi bóng đêm kinh khủng này.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:00:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm begging you...}{\i0}Làm ơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:00:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Whose voice is this?}Giọng này là?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It was only audible to me.}Chỉ mình tôi mới nghe thấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{A Yethma named Blaise is asking for help.}Một Yethma tên Blaise đang cầu cứu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Can you tell where she is?}Cô biết vị trí không?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Only that it's far off\Nin the distance, that way.}Hướng kia, ở phía xa...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{On the outskirts of town, huh?}Bên ngoài thị trấn à?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.51,0:01:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rossi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Naut, do you have an idea\Nwhere she might be?}{\i0}Naut, anh có biết vị trí cô ta không?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Not by a long shot.}Làm gì biết được.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess...}{\i0}Jess...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{A Yethma's inner voice can be heard\Nby someone of her own choosing, right?}{\i0}Giọng nói của Yethma sẽ được \Nnghe thấy bởi người cô ấy chọn nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's right.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, why can't Naut and I hear it directly?}{\i0}Vậy tại sao tôi và Naut không thể nghe nó trực tiếp?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If she's seeking help, shouldn't she be trying\Nto reach as many people as she can?}{\i0}Nếu muốn cứu thì phải cho càng \Nnhiều người nghe càng tốt chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Calling out indiscriminately\Ncould actually put her in danger.}Làm vậy sẽ càng khiến cô ta gặp nguy hiểm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{There could be\Nall kinds of reasons for that.}Ngoài kia không phải toàn người tốt thôi đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Anyway, the important thing is that...}Quan trọng hơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{there's a Yethma calling for help right now.}Yethma đó đang cầu cứu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess...}{\i0}Jess...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Have you tried reaching her yourself?}{\i0}Có thể truyền giọng nói tới cô ta chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes, I did try, but I'm not sure\Nif I've reached her or not.}Vâng, tôi đã thử. Nhưng không biết được không.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Listen to me...}{\i0}Nghe tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{both of you.}{\i0}cả hai người.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That wasn't the voice\Nof someone calling for help.}{\i0}Có thể giọng nói vừa rồi không phải cầu cứu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{An abstract appeal that doesn't even wait\Nfor a reply, on endless loop.}{\i0}Một lời cầu cứu vô vọng\N lặp lại mà không đợi phản hồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's like she's seeking salvation by praying.}{\i0}Cứ như cô ta đang cầu nguyện được cứu rỗi vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Then, isn't that...}Vậy thì mau
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{even more reason to rush to her rescue?}nhanh chóng cứu cô ta thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu làm thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{it turns out to be some kind of trap?}{\i0}sẽ dẫn đến một cái bẫy thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Someone could be using\Nthis sound of praying...}{\i0}Có kẻ nào đó lợi dụng lời cầu cứu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{to lure in another Yethma.}{\i0}để dụ một Yethma khác đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's entirely possible.}{\i0}Có khả năng đó lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{From inside that church?}{\i0}Bên trong nhà thờ đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes, I think so.}Vâng, có vẻ là vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That doesn't make sense.}Kì lạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I know it doesn't.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Pig...}Anh Heo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Originally, Yethmas were a race\Nwho prayed to the stars.}Thông thường, Yethma\N thường hay cầu nguyện các vì sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{So, we never enter churches.}Nên bọn tôi không vào nhà thờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is that right?}{\i0}Vậy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yethmas are forbidden from entering\Nany holy venue for prayer.}Yethma bị cấm vào cầu nguyện ở nơi linh thiêng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If you want to be precise.}Đó là sự thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Right.}{\i0}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm starting to see it.}{\i0}Tôi đã bắt đầu hiểu ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What could you want at this late hour?}Chuyện gì làm anh đến giờ này?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Sorry.}Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{This one said she could hear a voice\Ncoming from this church.}Nhỏ này nói là nghe thấy giọng từ nhà thờ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I started hearing the voice\Nof someone named Blaise...}Tôi nghe giọng của người tên Blaise...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{calling for help.}gọi cứu giúp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Well, that's odd!}Lạ nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{After all, there's no one here\Nin this church but me.}Nhà thờ này làm gì có ai ngoài ta?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Is that true?}Thật không?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Of course...}Thật...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{it's not as though\NI've actually patrolled the building.}Tuy ta cũng chưa kiểm tra lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If you need convincing...}Nếu cậu muốn kiểm tra...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{would you like to check for yourself?}thì cứ vào mà xem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You can't come in, you know.}Còn ngươi thì không.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm sorry, Jess.}{\i0}Xin lỗi Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I promise you, I'll make this work.}{\i0}Nhất định nó sẽ thành công.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{So...}Vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Rossi and I should just charge in\Nfrom the front, right?}Rossi và tôi sẽ tấn công thẳng vào?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{They might as well be holding\Na young Yethma girl hostage.}{\i0}Có thể chúng đang bắt Yethma làm con tin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It wouldn't do to make any reckless moves.}{\i0}Đừng làm gì bất cẩn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Excuse me!}À!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I... have an idea.}Tôi... có ý này.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh?}{\i0}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's not the same man as before.}{\i0}Một tên khác?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This smell... I've smelled it\Nin the lab at college.}{\i0}Mùi này... mình từng ngửi thấy hồi học đại học.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess! A man with an anesthetic\Nis coming toward you!}{\i0}Jess! Có một tên dùng thuốc mê đang tiếp cận!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Don't worry.}Đừng lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I didn't kill him.}Tôi không giết hắn đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess...}{\i0}Jess..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm sorry I put you in danger!}{\i0}Xin lỗi vì khiến cô gặp nguy hiểm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Come on, let's go!}Đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess...}{\i0}Jess...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{We're going to go save Blaise.}{\i0}Chúng ta sẽ đi cứu Blaise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes. Let's go.}Vâng, đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Where's the voice coming from?}Giọng nói ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{From under the floor.}Dưới sàn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Under the floor?}Dưới sàn?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This bloody smell!}{\i0}Có mùi máu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Just as I thought...}{\i0}Quả nhiên...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{it was the stench of blood!}{\i0}toàn là máu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If...}{\i0}Nếu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess had been captured\Nby that guy just now...}{\i0}Jess bị tên lúc nãy bắt được...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What are those?}{\i0}Kia là?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Are you Blaise?}Cô là Blaise à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Are you all right?}Có ổn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{A Yethma statue.}{\i0}Tượng Yethma?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The reason her inner voice\Nonly reached Jess was because...}{\i0}Lý do giọng nói chỉ chạm đến Jess là...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{her prayers were meant\Nfor Yethmas as a concept?}{\i0}cô ấy đã cầu nguyện bức tượng Yethma đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{We've come to save you.}Bọn tôi đến cứu cô đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You're safe now.}Mọi chuyện đã ổn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What's that letter?}{\i0}Lá thư đó là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{An indictment of all their misdeeds.}Báo cáo về hành vi của chúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{When we get back to town, I'm going to toss it\Ninto the dynasty's local base.}Khi quay lại thị trấn, tôi sẽ gửi \Nthẳng đến cơ quan luật pháp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I see.}{\i0}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If we'd charged in,\Nit might've put Jess in danger.}Nếu cứ thế lao vào, có thể làm Jess gặp nguy hiểm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thanks for your warning.}Cảm ơn vì đã cảnh báo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{We still haven't introduced\Nourselves, have we?}Giờ thì giới thiệu nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm Naut.}Tôi là Naut.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{This is Rossi.}Đây là Rossi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{My name is Jess.}Tôi là Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mong được giúp đỡ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And this is...}Và đây là...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Pig.}Anh Heo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Nice to meet you.}{\i0}Rất vui được gặp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cậu có tên mà nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I insist that you call me "Pig"!}{\i0}Hãy gọi anh đây là Heo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If I told her my real name...}{\i0}Nếu nói tên thật ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{there'd go my chance\Nof being called "Pig" by a girl!}{\i0}thì sao còn cơ hội để được gọi là heo chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I used to serve...}Tôi đã từng...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{the gravekeepers of Lyubori, House Esse.}là người gác mộ Lyubori, Nhà Essex.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I am Blaise, a Yethma.}Tên tôi là Blaise, một Yethma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{She said "used to serve." Meaning...}{\i0}Đã từng... tức là...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{this girl is another Yethma\Non her way to the royal capital?}{\i0}cũng là một cô gái đang trên đường đến thủ đô?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Y-You can go into more details tomorrow.}N-Ngày mai hãy kể lại chi tiết.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Do you think you can walk on your own?}Cô đi bộ được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{All right, then.}Được rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Let's get going!}Vậy đi nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{She's asleep now.}Cô ấy ngủ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Apparently, she was quite exhausted.}Có vẻ là khá mệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Is that right?}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You guys should get some rest, too.}Cả hai cũng nghỉ ngơi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ngày mai sẽ đi bộ cả ngày đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What's this?}Có chuyện gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You're awake already?}Đã dậy rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thank you for all that you did last night.}Cảm ơn vì chuyện đêm qua.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm so glad we were able to find you.}Tôi cũng thấy vui khi cứu được cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{We never would've noticed you...}Bọn tôi sẽ không biết được...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{from where we were\Nunless you prayed really intently.}nếu cô không cầu nguyện.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Not many people could pray\Nwith that much fervor for one thing only.}Không nhiều người có thể\N thành tâm cầu nguyện vậy đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You've got a strong soul.}Cô mạnh mẽ lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You take care of it.}Hãy giữ gìn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}{No Two Flowers are the Same}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thank you for all that you did for me.}Cảm ơn vì đã cứu giúp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I will never forget\Nhow indebted I am to you.}Tôi sẽ không bao giờ quên ơn huệ này.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Blaise, are you planning\Nto go to the royal capital on your own?}{\i0}Blaise, cô định một mình đến thủ đô hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I've thought it over.}{\i0}Tôi đang suy nghĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:15:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is there any way we can take Blaise\Nwith us to the royal capital?}{\i0}Có cách nào có thể dẫn Blaise đi cùng không?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'd also like to ask you to let her come.}Tôi cũng muốn thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Having one more person to guard...}Có thể một người phải bảo vệ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{puts Jess in that much more in danger.}sẽ đưa Jess vào tình thế nguy hiểm hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Are you okay with that?}Cậu thấy ổn với nó chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm well aware of the risks.}{\i0}Tôi biết rủi ro đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I know we'd be causing you trouble, but...}{\i0}Tôi biết sẽ gây rắc rối cho anh, nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{of course I'll do whatever I can, as well.}{\i0}tôi sẽ làm mọi việc trong khả năng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Is that so?}Thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{I was worried because it seems\Nlike she was being held captive for a while...}{\i0}Mình đã lo lắng vì cô ấy bị giam giữ một thời gian...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{but on the surface, at least,\NBlaise seems to be in good physical condition.}{\i0}nhưng bề ngoài có vẻ Blaise vẫn ổn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Unlike Jess, Blaise is reticent\Nand doesn't betray any sign of what she's feeling.}{\i0}Khác với Jess, Blaise chẳng hề bộc lộ chút cảm xúc nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{There's no question that as a race,}{\i0}Cũng chẳng hỏi han gì cả,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Yethmas are reserved, both in terms\Nof speaking style and personality.}{\i0}một Yethma dè dặt cả phong cách lẫn lời nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But that must be due to their social standing.}{\i0}Nhưng có lẽ là do địa vị xã hội.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Of course they each have\Ntheir own personality.}{\i0}Dĩ nhiên ai cũng có cá tính riêng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And most importantly...}{\i0}Và quan trọng hơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'd arbitrarily determined that Yethmas\Nwere reserved in terms of breasts, too...}{\i0}Mình đã tự tiện cho rằng Yethma sẽ có cùng tệp cỡ ngực...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{but apparently that was a misconception\Nbased on a small sample size.}{\i0}nhưng có vẻ đó là một quan niệm\N sai lầm dựa trên ngực cỡ nhỏ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Excuse me...}{\i0}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh?}{\i0}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Both Miss Blaise and I can hear\Neverything you're thinking.}{\i0}Cả tôi và Blaise đều có thể nghe thấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{My bad!}{\i0}Ấy chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I should've been more considerate!}{\i0}Tôi phải ý tứ hơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I feel terrible!}{\i0}Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That being said...}{\i0}Nói là thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Blaise doesn't seem to be bothered at all.\NShe's been like this throughout this journey.}{\i0}Blaise có vẻ không để ý lắm. \NCô ta đã như thế từ lúc đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I have a whole boatload\Nof questions for her, but...}{\i0}Mình muốn hỏi cô ấy lắm nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{- I don't mind. Really.\N- Huh?}{\i0}Không sao đâu.\N Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Go on and gaze at the one you like better.}{\i0}Anh cứ tiếp tục ngắm thứ mình thích đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{No! You've got it wrong!}{\i0}Không không! Hiểu lầm rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{I'm your chabirone, Jess!}{\i0}Tôi là Chabirone của Jess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{From here on in, I swear I'll never gaze\Nat anyone's breasts but yours!}{\i0}Từ giờ tôi xin thề sẽ không nhìn vếu ai khác ngoài Jess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:17:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I think I just came off\Nsounding like a pervert!}{\i0}Mình vừa ăn nói như thằng biến thái...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Please don't give it another thought.}{\i0}Không sao đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{After all, here in Mesteria, it stands to reason\Nthat men would prefer the larger ones.}{\i0}Dù sao thì ở Mesteria này\N đàn ông ai cũng thích to bự mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And to prove my point, look.}{\i0}Nhìn xem kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That guy...}{\i0}Tên đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess, I don't want you\Nto get the wrong idea!}{\i0}Jess, tôi không muốn cô hiểu lầm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The reason one's gaze\Nturns to the larger ones...}{\i0}Lý do người ta nhìn vào những thứ to lớn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{is the same reason why people tend to look\Nat sunflowers in bloom since they're taller!}{\i0}cũng như họ nhìn vào hoa hướng dương lúc nở rộ ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Sunflowers, did you say?}{\i0}Hoa hướng dương?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Even among those who turn their gazes\Ntoward the sunflowers,}{\i0}Dù có lỡ nhìn ngắm những \Nbông hoá hướng dương cao lớn,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{there are some who actually like\Nlittle violets better.}{\i0}nhưng vẫn có người thích hoa violet nhỏ bé phía dưới.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Back where I come from, the ones\Nwho preferred violets were the majority.}{\i0}Ở đất nước tôi thì những người đó đông lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Well, I'm very glad to hear that.}{\i0}V-Vậy thì tuyệt quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Maybe it's a stretch to call it "the majority"...}{\i0}Có lẽ hơi quá để gọi là đa số...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{but I'm sure you people can appreciate it!}{\i0}nhưng mọi người chắc chắn đánh giá cao nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The beauty of the violets\Nquietly blooming by the side of the road.}{\i0}Vẻ đẹp của những bông violet nở rộ ven đường.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Brother...}Anh ơi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{There you go. Have an apple.}Táo đây ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Oink?}{\i0}Éc?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:18:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Since you said we should have the kind\Nof relationship that siblings have, Mister Pig.}{\i0}Vì chúng ta có quan hệ anh em mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Oh, you mean last night?}{\i0}À đêm qua hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That was just an example, and there's no reason\Nto address me any differently.}{\i0}Cái đó chỉ là ví dụ thôi, không cần phải đổi cách gọi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Then, you'd rather\NI didn't call you "Brother"?}Vậy anh không thích gọi là anh trai ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{N-No!}{\i0}K-Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Well...}{\i0}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I guess...}{\i0}Tôi nghĩ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm actually not that averse to it.}{\i0}cũng không tệ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Here, Brother!}Đây, onii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Say "Aah!"}Aaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Aah!}{\i0}A!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You two...}Hai người...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What the heck are you doing?}Nãy giờ làm trò gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey, it's not what you think!}{\i0}Không phải như anh nghĩ đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm not a pervert who enjoys being called\N"Brother" by a younger, beautiful girl!}{\i0}Tôi không phải là thằng biến thái\N muốn gái xinh gọi là onii-san đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No, sir!}{\i0}Chắc chắn không!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Is that you introducing yourself?}Giới thiệu bản thân à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You like older sisters,\Ndon't you, Mister Naut?}Anh thích kiểu mấy chị gái ara nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I don't have an older sister!}Tôi không có chị gái!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Wait...}Ủa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{but last night, in your sleep,\Nyou were calling out "Big Sis" several times.}nhưng đêm qua anh nói mớ chị ơi chị ơi mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:19:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And you were begging\Nto put your head in her lap, right?}Và còn muốn được gối đầu lên đùi nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But if it wasn't your older sister,\Nthen who were you talking to?}Nhưng nếu không phải chị gái thì là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Pure curiosity can be so cruel sometimes.}{\i0}Trong sáng quá đôi khi cũng là cái tội...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Wh-Wh-Who cares who it was?}A-A-Ai mà cần chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's not as if the woman\NI had a crush on...}Nếu có chị gái nào đó cho tôi gối đầu lên
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{would coddle me when I called her "Big Sis"\Nand cradled my head in her lap!}rồi chiều chuộng tôi và xoa đầu nữa thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Th-That never happened, okay?}Chắc chắn sẽ không có chuyện đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is that you introducing yourself?}{\i0}Giới thiệu bản thân à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{All right, Jess!}{\i0}Rồi Jess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's enough of that.}{\i0}Bỏ chuyện đó qua một bên.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Also, since calling me "Brother" seems unhealthy\Nto me somehow, let's put an end to that, too.}{\i0}Vì cái gọi onii-san đó có thể \Ngây ghen tức nên dừng lại thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Are you sure? I'll be happy to try out as many\Ndifferent ways of addressing you as you like...}Vậy sao? Miễn là anh thích\N thì tôi gọi lúc nào cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{so please don't be shy about asking me!}Nên đừng ngần ngại nói ra nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Yeah, that would be great!}{\i0}À ừm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, this is...}{\i0}Đây là...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Right.}Phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{The Impaling Stones.}Rừng đá nhọn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{During the dark ages, a certain mage...}Vào thời kì hắc ám, một pháp sư...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{skewered hordes of people on these stones...}đã xiên kẻ thù trên những phiến đá này.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{and that's how it got its name.}Và cái tên bắt nguồn từ đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Well, apparently, there were\Nstrategic implications to that.}Mà, nó có ý nghĩa về chiến lược.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{One was to make the troops lying in ambush\Nlose their will to fight...}Nó khiến quân tấn công mất ý chí chiến đấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{and the other was to utilize the birds\Nmilling around the corpses...}Và lợi dụng lũ chim ăn xác.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{to detect the enemy's\Nmovements right away.}Để xác định vị trí của kẻ địch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Even a great mage\Nwho was unbeatable in direct combat...}Dù là một ma pháp sư vĩ đại...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{was afraid of being taken by surprise, I guess.}thì cũng phải sợ những đòn tấn công bất ngờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{In a place like this, there's no telling\Nwhere the enemy might be lurking, right?}Một nơi như này sẽ không biết kẻ thù đang nấp ở đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I have to say...}{\i0}Cơ mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Naut seems to be way more dependable\Nthan I ever thought.}{\i0}Naut có vẻ đáng tin cậy hơn mình nghĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Choosing a route\Nthat's safe from start to finish,}{\i0}Chọn một cung đường an toàn,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{the places he picks to rest up,\Neven the way he secures food for us...}{\i0}những nơi nghỉ qua đêm, cách đảm bảo lương thực...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{There's just no other way\Nto describe it but "spot on."}{\i0}Không có từ nào miêu tả ngoài từ "Tin cậy".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Making Rossi rest early so he can stand guard\Nduring the night... He has all his bases covered.}{\i0}Bắt Rossi nghỉ sớm để có thể canh chừng suốt đêm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You should get some sleep while you can.}Hãy ngủ khi có thể đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{He impressed me\Nduring that incident at the church...}{\i0}Anh ta khiến mình bất ngờ ở vụ nhà thờ đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{and it's not just his physical ability.}{\i0}và không chỉ sức mạnh thuần tuý...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{His leadership skills\Nare also a sight to see.}{\i0}Anh ta còn có kĩ năng lãnh đạo, quan sát.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I guess this means my turn is over now.}{\i0}Chắc chẳng tới lượt mình rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Not good!}{\i0}Không không!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm Jess's chabirone!}{\i0}Mình là Chabirone của Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I still have yet to...}{\i0}Vẫn còn phải...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's not over yet.}{\i0}Thế nên là...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{For someone living\Nin constant danger of death,}{\i0}Với người ngày nào cũng sống ở lằn ranh sinh tử,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{she looks so peaceful at rest.}{\i0}khuôn mặt lúc ngủ của Jess thật bình yên.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ra đây chút.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Tell me.}Cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Are you prepaređã săd to die?}Đã sẵn sàng tinh thần để chết chưa?
